removed_rules: ['IF a person shares experiences of going out with a group of friends and expresses happiness about it in a post THEN extraversion is likely High because it indicates enjoyment of social interactions.', 'IF a person expresses enthusiasm and engagement when talking about social gatherings, including specific phrases indicating positive experiences THEN extraversion is likely High because it shows eagerness to participate in social activities.']

['IF a person frequently mentions wanting to engage with friends and expresses a desire to make plans to see them again in the future THEN extraversion is likely High because it reflects a proactive approach to socializing.', 'IF a person exhibits enthusiastic language and a lot of expressive details in describing social events, including using vibrantly positive words THEN extraversion is likely High because it signifies a thrill in social interaction.']
